name: Froggies
public_notice: Froggies (FRGST) has recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. Visit this post for more information and visit the old token page here.
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: Froggies Token is created for the community, where we together as one build on a stable and vibrant token. We reward our holders, while building towards more utility and usability for everybody. Play to earn, buy to burn, hold to get rewarded, and utility that will make Froggies Token an interesting option for the now and the future to come. Read our roadmap and see what will bring Froggies Token and its Community to a higher level. To the Moon and Never Back
